'''圣斯德望堂'''（Chiesa di Santo Stefano）是一座[[天主堂|天主堂]]和曾经的[[主教座堂|主教座堂]]，位于[[意大利|意大利]]南部的[[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]]，供奉[[圣斯德望|圣斯德望]]，[[巴洛克建筑|巴洛克建筑]]，是[[卡普里|卡普里]]镇主要的彌撒场所。<ref name="capri.net">{{cite web|url=http://www.capri.net/en/churches|title=Capri The churches|publisher=Capri On Line|accessdate=2012-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618224456/http://www.capri.net/en/churches|archive-date=2012-06-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 环绕[[翁贝托一世广场|翁贝托一世广场]]的宗教建筑群建于17世纪，仅存的部分包括钟楼和总主教府（现在是市政厅）<ref name="Fodor's2004">{{cite book|author=Fodor's|title=Naples, Capri, and the Amalfi Coast|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=azspO-UEq8cC&pg=PA156|accessdate=2012-07-05|date=2004-02-01|publisher=Random House Digital, Inc.|isbn=978-1-4000-1311-1|pages=156–|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313053114/https://books.google.com/books?id=azspO-UEq8cC&pg=PA156|dead-url=no}}</ref>。圣斯德望堂建于1688-1697年，和[[圣公斯当休堂|圣公斯当休堂]]是岛上最古老的两座教堂<ref name="Knowles1918">{{cite book|last=Knowles|first=Sir Lees|title=The British in Capri, 1806-1808|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Z30IAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA25|accessdate=5 July 2012|edition=Public domain|year=1918|publisher=John Lane Company|pages=25–|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313051433/https://books.google.com/books?id=Z30IAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

